column1: UDIM 开始瓦片索引
UDIM 瓷砖烘焙范围的 UDIM 瓷砖索引。UDIM 烘焙范围用于定义 UDIM 瓷砖烘焙边界。烘烤结果只会影响指定范围的瓦片（起始瓦片索引 - 终止瓦片索引）
column2: UDIM tile index of UDIM tiles baking range.\nUDIMs baking range is used for defining UDIM tiles baking boundaries. Bake result will only affect specified range of tiles (Start Tile Index - End Tile Index)

column1: UDIM 结束瓦片索引
超级采样 AA
SSAA。通过在较高分辨率下进行烘焙，然后降频到较低分辨率来提高图像质量。有助于消除步进、锯齿和色彩区域边缘附近的巨大色差。
column2: SSAA. Improve image quality by baking at a higher resolution and then downscaling to a lower resolution. Helps removing stepping, jagging, and dramatic color difference near color area edges

column1: 升频
放大系数。以较低分辨率进行烘焙，然后按所选系数提升图像分辨率。这样可以缩短烘焙时间，获得更高分辨率，但要注意可能会出现模糊现象
column2: Upscaling factor. Bake at a lower resolution and upscale image resolution by the chosen factor after. Results in decreased baked time to get a higher resolution, but be aware that blurring might appear

column1: 烘焙样本
每个像素要渲染的样本数
column2: Number of samples to render per each pixel

column1: 自适应采样
根据估计的噪点水平自动减少每个像素的采样数量
column2: Automatically reduce the number of samples per pixel based on estimated noise level

column1: 噪音阈值
停止采样的噪声水平阈值，数值越低，噪声越小，但渲染时间越长。
column2: Noise level step to stop sampling at, lower values reduce noise at the cost of render time.\nZero for automatic setting based on number of AA sampled

column1: 最小采样烘焙
在应用自适应采样之前，像素接收的最小采样数目。当设置为 0（默认值）时，它会自动设置为由噪点阈值决定的值。
column2: The minimum number of samples a pixel receives before adaptive sampling is applied. When set to 0 (default), it is automatically set to a value determined by the Noise Threshold
